############# TOMCAT SETUP

Install Tomcat 

# Normal Installation procedure (To start Tomcat)
    1. Goto folder Tomcat/bin : Click on startup.bat or startup.sh
    2. Goto CMD Tomcat/bin : Click on startup.bat or startup.sh
    3. 1. Goto folder Tomcat/bin : Catelina.out start

# To Stop Server
  1. Goto folder Tomcat/bin : Click on shutdown.bat or shutdown.sh
  2. Goto CMD Tomcat/bin : Click on shutdown.bat or shutdown.sh
  3. 1. Goto folder Tomcat/bin : Catelina.out stop
  
## Configure Port:
  <Tomcat install>/ conf/server.xml
  Connector Port="8080" default value
  change to required port number
  restart tomcat
  
## How to run an application
<InstallDir Tomcat> / webapps/
Put .war file inside the webapps folder e.g Jenkin.war
restart tomcat


  
